				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/B%C3%A0ng-gi%E1%BA%A3i-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-L%C3%A2m-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/poem-qILOwFSCVvPsPMcGQcUMJw">Bàng giải vịnh - Lâm Đại Ngọc - 螃蟹詠－林黛玉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/B%E1%BB%95-x%C3%A0-gi%E1%BA%A3-thuy%E1%BA%BFt/poem-6rOlVuds9Kh1YCFFEgqOPQ">Bổ xà giả thuyết - 捕蛇者說</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-cFCa0wn9ZwJZJ5nwtlsQmQ">Liễu Tông Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-L%C3%A3m/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Tri%E1%BB%81u-v%C3%A3n-b%E1%BA%A1c-H%E1%BB%97-gi%C3%A1-th%E1%BB%9Di-t%C3%A1c/poem-rCwYhjmMweEOgy-PIpXtZw">Đông Triều vãn bạc (Hỗ giá thời tác) - 東潮晚泊（扈駕時作）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-L%C3%A3m/author-11a_esS_09VNjvlkNmasVQ">Vũ Lãm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B3-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c-Kim/H%E1%BB%97n-%C4%91%E1%BB%99n-th%E1%BA%A1ch-h%C3%A0nh/poem-fbq20d63GkVQtdMcT0iseQ">Hỗn độn thạch hành - 渾沌石行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B3-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c-Kim/author-fE-hTNUiNUqZvp4Llo1zqA">Phó Nhược Kim</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/Nh%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BA%AFc-hi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-VYasO4wFAO6exBskUh6-Qw">Nhập tắc hiếu - 入則孝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/author-Q1iBAvdMoGVZdNIyHAuy-w">Lý Dục Tú</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Ph%C3%B9-Phong-h%C3%A0o-s%C4%A9-ca/poem-3VA4D7IRvvruv2gGIxG8GA">Phù Phong hào sĩ ca - 扶風豪士歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A1-Nghi%C3%AAm-trung-th%E1%BB%ABa-t%E1%BB%91ng-Thanh-Th%C3%A0nh-s%C6%A1n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-s%C4%A9-nh%C5%A9-t%E1%BB%ADu-nh%E1%BA%A5t-b%C3%ACnh/poem-M7tTFCwFjmV1N4pdibJ92w">Tạ Nghiêm trung thừa tống Thanh Thành sơn đạo sĩ nhũ tửu nhất bình - 謝嚴中丞送青城山道士乳酒一瓶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/T%E1%BA%B7ng-L%E1%BA%A1ng-Giang-gi%C3%A1o-th%E1%BB%A5-L%C3%AA-chi-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Kh%C3%AA-tri-huy%E1%BB%87n/poem-wgBh9QYrFsscBrAfgqhCHg">Tặng Lạng Giang giáo thụ Lê chi Hương Khê tri huyện - 贈涼江教授黎之香溪知縣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/T%E1%BA%A9u-b%C3%BAt-t%E1%BA%A1-M%E1%BA%A1nh-gi%C3%A1n-ngh%E1%BB%8B-k%C3%BD-t%C3%A2n-tr%C3%A0/poem-cwd22cTED0FtlMGOAisk5w">Tẩu bút tạ Mạnh gián nghị ký tân trà - 走筆謝孟諫議寄新茶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-u9rcZBkvQdaFAifcr_6CMA">Lư Đồng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/V%E1%BB%8Dng-t%E1%BA%A7m/poem-Tmhikkfi_oJ_CgPmuaeU3g">Vọng tầm - 望尋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/author-5S8czaSOqXhHlNE7NtKr8g">Đặng Trần Côn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
